  "root_text": {
    "iti14:0.1": "Itivuttaka 14 ",
    "iti14:0.2": "Ekakanipāta ",
    "iti14:0.3": "Dutiyavagga ",
    "iti14:0.4": "Avijjānīvaraṇasutta ",
    "iti14:1.1": "Vuttañhetaṁ bhagavatā vuttamarahatāti me sutaṁ: ",
    "iti14:2.1": "“Nāhaṁ, bhikkhave, aññaṁ ekanīvaraṇampi samanupassāmi yena nīvaraṇena nivutā pajā dīgharattaṁ sandhāvanti saṁsaranti yathayidaṁ, bhikkhave, avijjānīvaraṇaṁ. ",
    "iti14:2.2": "Avijjānīvaraṇena hi, bhikkhave, nivutā pajā dīgharattaṁ sandhāvanti saṁsarantī”ti. ",
    "iti14:2.3": "Etamatthaṁ bhagavā avoca. ",
    "iti14:2.4": "Tatthetaṁ iti vuccati: ",
    "iti14:3.1": "“Natthañño ekadhammopi, ",
    "iti14:3.2": "yenevaṁ nivutā pajā; ",
    "iti14:3.3": "Saṁsaranti ahorattaṁ, ",
    "iti14:3.4": "yathā mohena āvutā. ",
    "iti14:4.1": "Ye ca mohaṁ pahantvāna, ",
    "iti14:4.2": "tamokhandhaṁ padālayuṁ; ",
    "iti14:4.3": "Na te puna saṁsaranti, ",
    "iti14:4.4": "hetu tesaṁ na vijjatī”ti. ",
    "iti14:5.1": "Ayampi attho vutto bhagavatā, iti me sutanti. ",
    "iti14:5.2": "Catutthaṁ. "
  },
  "translation_text": {
    "iti14:0.1": "So It Was Said 14 ",
    "iti14:0.2": "The Book of the Ones ",
    "iti14:0.3": "Chapter Two ",
    "iti14:0.4": "The Shroud of Ignorance ",
    "iti14:1.1": "This was said by the Buddha, the Perfected One: that is what I heard. ",
    "iti14:2.1": "“Mendicants, I do not see a single shroud, shrouded by which people wander and transmigrate for a long time like the shroud of ignorance. ",
    "iti14:2.2": "Shrouded by ignorance, people wander and transmigrate for a long time.” ",
    "iti14:2.3": "The Buddha spoke this matter. ",
    "iti14:2.4": "On this it is said: ",
    "iti14:3.1": "“There is no other thing ",
    "iti14:3.2": "that shrouds people like ignorance. ",
    "iti14:3.3": "Veiled by delusion, ",
    "iti14:3.4": "they transmigrate day and night. ",
    "iti14:4.1": "Those who have given up delusion, ",
    "iti14:4.2": "shattering the mass of darkness, ",
    "iti14:4.3": "wander no more, ",
    "iti14:4.4": "the root is not found in them.” ",
    "iti14:5.1": "This too is a matter that was spoken by the Blessed One: that is what I heard. "
  },
  "variant_text": {
    "iti14:2.1": "yena → yenevaṁ (?) | avijjānīvaraṇaṁ → avijjānīvaraṇena (?) ",
    "iti14:3.2": "yenevaṁ → yeneva (si, pts-vp-pli1, mr) ",
